4. Article 2 of the Principal Order is amended by the insertion of: 

““Act of 2024” means the Local Government (Mayor of Limerick) and 
Miscellaneous Provisions Act 2024 (No. 7 of 2024); 

“Limerick City and County Council” shall be construed as in accordance with 
subsection (3) of section 11 of, and Part 3 of Schedule 5 to, the Local 
Government Act 2001; 

“mayor” and “Mayor of Limerick” has the meaning assigned to it by section 9 
of the Act of 2024; 

 “chief executive” shall, in the case of Limerick City and County Council, read 
as “director general”; 

